amma$-ray to total shock soft-to-hard X-ray fluxes.\nThis stability criterion implies an unbroken extension of X-ray power-law\nemission to hundreds of keV for some systems. We explore observational\ndiscriminants between the gas-dominated and magnetospheric scenarios,\nmotivating contemporaneous radio through $\\gamma$-ray monitoring of these\nsystems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Oct 2018 18:37:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-26"}
