station of the free-energy minimization of quasi-2D layers, eventually\naffected by factors such as the interplane stacking, the interaction with\nmolecules and/or with the AFM tip.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 Oct 2018 11:02:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-01"}
